Olden v1.01 runtime system

Martin C. Carlisle
June 1996

see COPYRIGHT notice in olden_v1.01/COPYRIGHT

files:
Makefile - to use visualization, uncomment -DVISUALIZE
accumulate - sums profiling information from multiple processors into
             single total (input: prof.{job id}.pn[0-num_pes]
                           output: prof.{job id}.all)
affinity.h - macros for having profiler compute affinities
cache.[ch],cache_asm.asm, cache_handlers.c - caching routines
collect.awk - used by accumulate
constants.h 
debug.c - debugging routines
future-cell.h, future.asm - code for FUTUREs.
init.c - initialization/shutdown routines
mccvis.asm - interface routines for Olden visualization
mem-ref.h - standard header file for Olden programs
mem.c - mymalloc routines
migrate.[ch],migrate_asm.asm - migration routines
msg.[ch],msg2.c - core of runtime system
plain-mem.c,plain.c,plain2.asm - used for plain versions of Olden programs
prof.c,prof_asm.asm - routines used to collect profiling information
registers.h - header file for Olden reserved registers
stack.asm,stack_frame.h - stack routines
threads.h - header file for blocked threads
